{"tid":93764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實做港豬都幾開心","createTime":"2017-01-24T16:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T09:08:55.000Z","uid":68846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a766a29a7732baa95e22d8c6b2e9dc5e82233ff0","tid":93764,"uid":68846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:10:59.000Z","msg":"日日見到d新聞都好撚嬲<br />\n做港豬日日吃喝玩樂<br />\n見到d新聞自已又做唔到d咩真係好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前去既遊行而家諗返都覺得好哂氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港豬咩都唔撚洗理 自已道德又站係不敗之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對香港未來冇希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係做返條精蟲 讀完書出 揾到份夠我食既工 直到我既壽命完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0530b4895abd20036476446fc042209505ffc235","tid":93764,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac3a170bf6bf5a7b2e60b2e5034c5c0d3e11c5d","tid":93764,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"得閒share 下支那好聲音 睇下支那劇 奔跑吧兄弟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"c58463d6145599c5fada12dbb520f620a9c91ef3","tid":93764,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"愛思索便會福薄<br />\n飲飽吃醉是容易極的快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b5dfb2fb3a662081c31a738bd56220e70a7273","tid":93764,"uid":9681,"like":0,